git.commitMessage: v1.0.9.070625 Is it possible to have a unique version number that appears on the app? Can the dev version number from which it is derived be shown on the deployment version somehow. The deployment version says "v1.0.3.070625", which is fine but the dev version says "main@dev-6-162205". I was hoping it would say "v1.0.2.070625" or whatever version it was based on.
